{"service_name": "ServiceNow (SaaS) Solution Accelerators Service Asset and Configuration Management (CMDB)", "service_id": "7480114731389549", "company_name": "KPMG LLP", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     KPMG LLP\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     ServiceNow (SaaS) Solution Accelerators Service Asset and Configuration Management (CMDB)\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Our SACM (CMDB) \u2018Solution Accelerator\u2019 combines rapid application customisation methodology with KPMG\u2019s ITIL ServiceNow framework. Considerably reducing customisation time by leveraging CMDB customisation templates and CI data-load templates. Enabling your organisation to leverage the current and historical configuration data of all your IT assets.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Dedicated project team and access to KPMG\u2019s ServiceNow accredited resources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     PMO - Agile deployment methodology\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compatible with existing ServiceNow environments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Customisation and configuration templates, ITIL aligned and KPMG best practice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ITIL and KPMG best practice process workflows and artefacts\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CMDB Data Model - Outline service model\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Requirements gathering, Project management, Test management and Implementation services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deployment sourcing of your choice, internal team and/or KPMG\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Tailored ServiceNow CMDB solution to suit your specific organisational needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Low cost customisation methodology, Agile approach utilising KPMG\u2019s KGS resources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Simplified transition and adoption, Process documentation templates and knowledge artefacts\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ServiceNow configuration and customisation templates, ITIL aligned and best practice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Configuration Item and Attribute templates, Quick and efficient data-loading\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compatible with existing customised ServiceNow environments, Test plan templates included\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3250 per person\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93303/7480114731389549-pricing-document-2015-10-06-0945.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93303/7480114731389549-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-06-0945.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmark